data.description: This charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is located in the heart of Crawfordsville, and is priced to move! Built in 1900 and 2688 sf., this home retains much of its original character, and a gorgeous double-sided fireplace is the first thing you will notice when you step inside. Natural light floods the home, and original woodwork still present adds to the historic charm.  If you are looking for a great investment opportunity, this home is a must-see! Motivated Seller!!
